┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    FOUNDATIONAL SPECTRUM MATRIX                      │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

LAYER 1: SERIALIZATION & TRANSPORT
├─ TypeCore: State Externalization
├─ Specs: {format, schema, encoding, transport, batch-processing}
├─ Function: Internal → External Representation
└─ Directionality: Content Outbound

LAYER 2: INFORMATION ACCESS & QUERY
├─ TypeCore: Knowledge Retrieval & Relation
├─ Specs: {syntax, scope, filters, ranking, depth, temporal-bounds}
├─ Function: Stored State → Accessible Knowledge
└─ Directionality: Knowledge Inbound/Navigational

LAYER 3: PRESENTATION & RENDERING
├─ TypeCore: Perceptual Interface
├─ Specs: {layout, encoding, device-target, accessibility, parsing}
├─ Function: Accessible Knowledge → Consumable Form
└─ Directionality: Content to Sensory/Computational Interface

┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                     SPECTRUM FLOW TOPOLOGY                          │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

UNIDIRECTIONAL CASCADE (Sequential):
Internal State 
  ↓ [Serialization specs applied]
  ↓ Serialized Content
  ↓ [Query specs applied]
  ↓ Retrieved/Related Knowledge
  ↓ [Rendering specs applied]
  ↓ Perceptual/Computational Output

BIDIRECTIONAL COUPLING (Recursive):
Rendering constraints ← inform → Serialization choices
Query depth → determines → Serialization granularity
Transport capacity ← limits
→ Rendering resolution

